      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פרוטה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>אֱלֹהֵיהֶם עַל הֶהָרִים.</b></big> תימה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דייק הכי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בפרק",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "השולח (גיטין דף",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לו.) דאמר רשב\"ג תקנה גדולה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "התקינו שיהיו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "העדים מפרשין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שמותיהן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בגיטין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כו'",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ובהגוזל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קמא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "(<a href=\"/bava_kamma/103b\">ב&quot;ק דף קג:</a>) א\"ר אליעזר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בר צדוק תקנה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גדולה התקינו שאם היתה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "היציאה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "יתירה על הקרן כו' וי\"ל דהתם קרי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליה גדולות לפי שהיה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בה צורך גדול והכא דייק",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מדאמר שנו כאן <big><b>עקרוה</b></big>. אף על גב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דכופר הכל פטור דלא נתקנה שבועת היסת עד בימי רב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נחמן מ\"מ על בעל הבית שייכא טפי ועוד דאפילו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "במודה במקצת שדיוה אשכיר <big><b>בעל הבית</b></big>.",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולא פלוג בין פועל אחד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליש לו פועלים הרבה ובירושלמי קאמר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עסקיו מרובין <big><b>וניתב ליה</b></big>. וא\"ת ולא יהא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ברי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "של בעל הבית אלא כאיני יודע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "והניחא למ\"ד בהשואל (<a href=\"/bava_metzia/97b\">ב&quot;מ דף צז:</a>) ברי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עדיף אלא למ\"ד לאו ברי עדיף",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אמאי וי\"ל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דהוי כמנה לי בידך והלה אומר איני יודע אם החזרתיו לך דחייב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לכ\"ע כדמוכח בהגוזל בתרא (<a href=\"/bava_kamma/118a\">ב&quot;ק דף קיח.</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וא\"ת אכתי אמאי ניתיב ליה בלא שבועה וכי אי אפשר להיות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בשום פעם שיהיה ברי שלו טוב דפעמים יהיה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כדבריו דהא רבי יהודה לא מיחייב אלא בהודאה במקצת וי\"ל דנהי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דרבי יהודה לא חשיב לגמרי כאיני יודע רבנן מיהא חשבי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליה כודאי שכח <big><b>כדי</b></big>. הכא ודאי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שהוא עומד וצוח שפרע שייך תקנה כדי להפיס",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דעתו אבל בההיא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דהגוזל בתרא (שם) דקאמר איני יודע אם החזרתיו לך אין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צריך לתקן <big><b>אפילו</b></big>. וא\"ת והא ה\"ל כאיני יודע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אם גזלתיך דפטרי רב נחמן ורבי יוחנן בהגוזל בתרא (שם) ובהשואל (<a href=\"/bava_metzia/97b\">ב&quot;מ דף צז:</a>) וי\"ל דהתם",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא מודה מידי אבל הכא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שמודה במקצת ה\"ל כמנה לי בידך והלה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אומר אין לך בידי אלא נ' ונ' לא ידענא דאמרינן התם מתוך שאינו יכול לישבע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משלם <big><b>קציצה</b></big>. לא קאמר המע\"ה ואי לא מייתי ראיה מפסיד אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ישבע בעה\"ב ויפסיד אומן כדאמר לקמן וא\"ת ולישני ליה כגון ששכרו שלא בעדים ונאמן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מתוך שיכול לומר לא שכרתיך",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מעולם כדאמרי' בסמוך וי\"ל דשאני הכא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמודה במקצת לא היה יכול להעיז",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולכפור הכל אי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "880px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נמי דלקמן מוקי לה בשכרו בעדים דומיא דרישא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 45a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    }
  ]
}